    &lt;h1&gt;Wedding Invitation Design&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;p class=&quot;meta&quot;&gt;July 02, 2015&lt;/p&gt;



    &lt;p class=&quot;drop-cap-p&quot;&gt;A few months ago I undertook the important task of designing Wedding Invitations for my sister and her now husband. (woo weddings!)&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;I delved into what I needed to know to make it.&lt;/p&gt;
