    &lt;p&gt;Although, I am lucky to have a sister who&#39;s upfront with what she wants. She wanted the invitations to be like Boarding Passes.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;*Begins the research into boarding passes.&lt;/p&gt;
